data.description:
Lovely East Side three bedroom apartment with tall ceilings, and original hardwoods and crown moulding throughout. Kitchen features stainless appliances, two sinks with disposals, and dishwasher. Apartment includes two full tile baths, central AC, and in unit laundry! Walking distance to Downtown Providence, Amtrak, Brown and RISD, Whole Foods, Starbucks and more! Easy highway access to Rt. 95.

One year lease. Available July 1st. No smoking or pets.
